{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Terra Avoider is a 2.5D shooter in which the player must survive through difficult, arena based boss encounters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The player has a number of tools at their disposal to inflict destruction on the invaders and to avoid annihilation at their hands, or whatever they have in place of hands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dodge - Increases speed and become immune for a split second.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Time Dilation - Slows down the passage of time for a brief period.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Recharging shield - Absorbs a hit, causing the player to become immune for a couple of seconds afterwards. This also adds a multiplier to the speed of your weapon up to 5 times.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Overheat Venting (Active reload) - Successful 'reloads' release a powerful plasma orb, whilst also adding 1/5th of a charge towards the player's shield This also increases the ship's rate of fire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hard mode and level select - Unlocked after game completion.\u00a0</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customizable key bindings and sound mixer.</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"GuardiaGone","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2674510/8524e6c7934047786ba9ce4c63faee7590976602.jpg"},{"name":"Heartless","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2674510/eafd95a4ca662349a71ee805a4cf2585582c3c6b.jpg"},{"name":"Without Rule","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2674510/a3c2f9c01fc2b964d476904bdb6324d54208ddc2.jpg"},{"name":"The Guhardian","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/st